title: Full Show (Lakers win in OT, Cowboys RB coach comments on Zeke vs Tony Pollard, Kyrie apologizes)
description:
00:00 LeBron and Lakers beat Pelicans 120-117 in OT
21:53 Cowboys RB coach calls Zeke and Pollard a “sledgehammer and a sword”
58:35 Kyrie Irving apologizes and takes “responsibility” for controversial posts
1:09:19 Astros throw a combined no hitter to even the World Series at 2-2 against the Phillies and a discussion of LeBron’s 20 point performance in win over Pelicans
1:22:47 Nets reportedly finalizing Ime Udoka as next HC
1:34:12 Dan Quinn comments on the best way to use Micah Parsons
1:43:44 LeBron goes 0-7 from three last night
1:50:54 Are the Packers sending a message to Aaron Rodgers with quiet trade deadline?
1:54:45 Luka Dončić hits milestone for the first time since Wilt Chamberlain
